<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>القَزَعُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ عَنِ القَزَعِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>» <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) وَهُوَ: حَلْقُ بَعْضِ الشَّعْرِ وَتَرْكُ بَعْضِهِ.<br>(٢) مُتَّفَقٌ عَلَيْهِ.</p> </div>